    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Increase one ability score of your choice by 1, to a maximum of 30.</p><p><strong>Fortified Health.</strong> Your Hit Point maximum increases by 40. In addition, whenever you regain Hit Points, you can regain additional Hit Points equal to your Constitution modifier (currently [[lookup @abilities.con.mod]]). Once you've regained these additional Hit Points, you can't do so again until the start of your next turn.</p><section id=\"secret-JgTurTuyg5ikUyQq\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This feat includes an Active Effect which will automatically apply the bonus to your maximum HP.</p><p>The <strong>Fortify Health</strong> activity includes the additional healing.</p></section>",
